          "recordId": "a1b39a05-8e32-4f67-869b-5b208381b5ec",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "interactions ",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-a654dbf0-0b27-4678-8032-9db141e153b3",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "a654dbf0-0b27-4678-8032-9db141e153b3",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "1. Our highest priority is to satisfy the customer through early and continuous delivery of valuable software.",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-21756b8b-bab6-485e-8de3-2ae4dd0a3026",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "21756b8b-bab6-485e-8de3-2ae4dd0a3026",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "2. Welcome changing requirements, even late in  development. Agile processes harness change for  the customer's competitive advantage.",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-f655e0cb-7761-4a29-9deb-8e300b4fa146",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "f655e0cb-7761-4a29-9deb-8e300b4fa146",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "3. Deliver working software frequently, from a  couple of weeks to a couple of months, with a  preference to the shorter timescale.",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-bdc25d56-cfce-4381-8dc1-78a1f9047f3d",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "bdc25d56-cfce-4381-8dc1-78a1f9047f3d",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "4. Business people and developers must work  together daily throughout the project.",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-2b222efb-649a-4097-9e14-47feb8524725",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "2b222efb-649a-4097-9e14-47feb8524725",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "5. Build projects around motivated individuals.  Give them the environment and support they need,  and trust them to get the job done.",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-624e5e7d-73c6-469b-a092-ff896faea0f3",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "624e5e7d-73c6-469b-a092-ff896faea0f3",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "6. The most efficient and effective method of  conveying information to and within a development  team is face-to-face conversation.",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-441941b6-c128-4702-9cc0-6892af7d1520",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "441941b6-c128-4702-9cc0-6892af7d1520",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "7. Working software is the primary measure of progress.",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-f05186e5-b26c-449c-8084-73ef9f1fe915",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "f05186e5-b26c-449c-8084-73ef9f1fe915",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "8. Agile processes promote sustainable development.  The sponsors, developers, and users should be able  to maintain a constant pace indefinitely.",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-9456b8b2-7692-462b-9551-99bba832e0cf",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "9456b8b2-7692-462b-9551-99bba832e0cf",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "9. Continuous attention to technical excellence  and good design enhances agility.",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-b7cf4ee5-f0cd-4a59-8e71-7c33c633b310",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "b7cf4ee5-f0cd-4a59-8e71-7c33c633b310",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "10. Simplicity – the art of maximizing the amount  of work not done – is essential.",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-437ebe49-1541-40b3-8b5e-de4ad987a112",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "437ebe49-1541-40b3-8b5e-de4ad987a112",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "11. The best architectures, requirements, and designs  emerge from self-organizing teams.",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-b1082889-c7ab-4384-b24a-834fec4817a5",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "b1082889-c7ab-4384-b24a-834fec4817a5",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "12. At regular intervals, the team reflects on how  to become more effective, then tunes and adjusts  its behavior accordingly.",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-71b4a705-4c22-460e-8044-6d9c0c0f9bd0",
          "collection": "elements",
          "recordId": "71b4a705-4c22-460e-8044-6d9c0c0f9bd0",
          "field": "name",
          "value": "It's all about priority!",
          "message": "El nombre debe ser claro, legible y comenzar con mayúscula."
        },
        {
          "id": "nomenclatura_regla-7632c7e4-368e-46b9-8150-e11087b7cbb2",
